coverage.graph

Class GraphAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • coverage.graph.GraphAdapter

  • public class GraphAdapter
extends java.lang.Object
    It is for applet. It is adapter from coverage.graph.Graph to edu.uci.ics.jung.graph.Graph. It is used to visualize the graph based one Jung api package. Jung API package can be downloaded from jung site
    Author:
    wuzhi Modifeid and Corrected by Nan Li Start Date: March 4, 2009
